1️⃣2️⃣ Real Production Architecture (Multi AZ)
Professional companies use multiple availability zones.

                Internet
                    │
             Internet Gateway
                    │
        ┌────────────┴────────────┐
        │                         │
   Public Subnet AZ1        Public Subnet AZ2
        │                         │
      Load Balancer (ALB)
        │                         │
   Private Subnet AZ1        Private Subnet AZ2
        │                         │
      App Server              App Server
        │                         │
     Database Replica       Database Primary
Benefits:

High availability
Fault tolerance
Auto scaling

